                                PortageLive
                         Runtime translation server

This directory contains the files you need to install a trained Portage system
on a translation server.  We call this PortageLive.  Please read the
"PortageLive Manual" section of the Portage 1.5 User Manual for instructions.

Contents:
   bin/         tools to build the PortageLive runtime software layout
   models/      tools to build the PortageLive models layout
   www/         web service software, and tools to install it
   scripts/     scripts shared between all of the above
   va/          specific documentation for creating a PortageLive Virtual
                Appliance - don't start here, it won't make sense until you
                read the PortageLive Manual.
   python/      tools to create a custom python package for PortageLive VMs
